      <DefaultText>Fatebinder [Player Name],

Forgive me the curtness of this rushed missive - the matter is too urgent for the luxury of formalities. 

I know that you braved the flaming ruins of the [url=glossary:vellum citadel]Vellum Citadel[/url]. 

The Archive - Did you find it? Is it safe?

- Rhogalus</DefaultText>
