      <ID>30</ID>
      <DefaultText>Fatebinder [Player Name],

Better perhaps, then consigning it forever to the flame. I weep at what lore will be lost when the Overlord finally sees fit to extinguish the Voices. Consider that before you next feed it your knowledge. 

It is in the Voices' nature to overreach, for it is never sated. One day, its hunger will turn towards the Overlord, and on that day, [url=glossary:the voices of nerat]the Voices of Nerat[/url] will have outlived its usefulness to [url=glossary:kyros]Kyros[/url].

- Fatebinder Rhogalus</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
